        <item>
            <title>香港攝影大賽得獎結果公佈，南昌押霓虹招牌拆前「遺作」獲選佳作</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/hong-kong-photo-contest/dc/photogism/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=hong-kong-photo-contest</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/hong-kong-photo-contest/dc/photogism/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蔣納偲]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:00:29 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[攝影文化]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[香港攝影大賽]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1222816</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《國家地理》雜誌舉辦的 2023 年香港攝影大賽昨日揭曉，展現了來自各行各業攝影愛好者的精彩視角。此次大賽共吸引了 9,205 件作品參賽，涵蓋城市、生態、風景、人物、歷史建築以及手機攝影六大類別。評審團由國際及本地的攝影大師組成，包括國家地理資深生態攝影師 Tim Laman、香港知名攝影藝術家鄭振揚，以及《國家地理》中文版的總編輯李永適。</p><p>在各類別中尤其引人注目的是歷史建築組別，其中一幅以昔日深水埗南昌押的霓虹招牌為主題的作品，記錄了這個標誌性景象的最後光輝。這幅名為《南昌押》的照片由朱偉民拍攝，展示了南昌押那不再復見的霓虹招牌。值得一提的是，南昌押的霓虹招牌因不符合現行的《建築物條例》而於去年 3 月被拆除，此後由保育團體「霓虹交匯」在元朗負責保存。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222819" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-10.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>歷史建築組別的冠軍作品則是由陳潔冰創作的《人生路》，這幅作品巧妙地捕捉了黃大仙祠的獨特面貌，向我們展示了香港豐富的文化遺產和攝影師們如何通過鏡頭將這些瞬間永久地定格。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222832" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11-694x495.png" alt="" width="694" height="495" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11-694x495.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-11.png 1261w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>以下部分參賽作品：</h2><p>風景組：</p><p>冠軍作品：《動力之源》金冠華</p><p><img decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-12.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亞軍作品：《霧上航行》謝漢明</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13-694x464.png" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13-694x464.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-13.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季軍作品：《大佛雲霧繚繞》張貽彬</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222845" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14-694x463.png" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14-694x463.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-14.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>城市組：</p><p>冠軍作品：《天梯》黃建榮</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222846" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-15.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亞軍作品：《樂園》翟廣文</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16-694x459.png" alt="" width="694" height="459" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16-694x459.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-16.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季軍作品：《旺角街頭》田雋愷</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17-381x580.png" alt="" width="381" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17-381x580.png 381w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-17.png 592w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 381px" /></p><p>歷史建築組：</p><p>冠軍作品：《人生路》陳潔冰</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222849" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18-694x554.png" alt="" width="694" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18-694x554.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-18.png 1127w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>亞軍作品：《撐傘人》李健陶</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19-694x555.png" alt="" width="694" height="555" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19-694x555.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-19.png 1126w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>季軍作品：《我在明，你在暗！》陳輝</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1222851" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20-442x580.png" alt="" width="442" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20-442x580.png 442w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/screenshot20240306at-20.png 685w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 442px" /></p><p>其餘的得獎作品可以透過<a href="https://hkphotocontest.com/exhibition.asp">網上虛擬展覽形式</a>免費參觀，或由即日起至 3 月 24 日都可以於線下參加實體展覽：九龍尖沙咀海港城廣東道 23 號太子酒店 3 樓 SAVVY。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%96%E8%BC%AF%EF%BD%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%A4%A7%E8%B3%BD%E7%B5%90%E6%9E%9C%E5%87%BA%E7%88%90-%E5%8D%97%E6%98%8C%E6%8A%BC%E9%9C%93%E8%99%B9%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E6%B8%85%E6%8B%86%E5%89%8D%E3%80%8C%E9%81%BA%E7%85%A7%E3%80%8D%E7%8D%B2%E9%81%B8%E4%BD%B3%E4%BD%9C%EF%BD%9Cyahoo-032926223.html?guccounter=1">Yahoo</a>、<a href="https://hkphotocontest.com/exhibition.asp">National Geographic</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/06/hong-kong-photo-contest/dc/photogism/">香港攝影大賽得獎結果公佈，南昌押霓虹招牌拆前「遺作」獲選佳作</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
